      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CADILLAC EXPRESS (4) shows ability but remains a maiden after eight starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing sixth (18.13) at this track. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can make amends. FRENCH BLONDE (2) was sent out at big odds from this same box last time but ran above herself when a neck second (17.73) at this track in Maiden. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Expecting another bold showing. PICK A CADILLAC (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (18.33) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Can find the frame this time. LITTLE BUTTON (6) makes debut for the Sandra Elmes kennel. Betting to provide the best guide to her chances.",
